pageContext.description: Dimensions: EL 158.2mm; max E W bl. 41mm; T socket at bread 1.3-2.6mm; EDS>111.5,Typology: fairly flattened rounded midrib; tapering blade wings with traces of edge bevels,Condition: edges mainly irreg. sharp due to corrosion, main break and hole in socket midrib probably all ancient; letter probably due to thinness of cg.; tip fairly rounded in profile.,Attached Material: Fragments of wood shaft stuck to s. inside.
